    <li><strong>Forex</strong> - Currency markets, exchange rates, technical analysis</li>
    <li><strong>Crypto</strong> - Bitcoin, Ethereum, altcoins, blockchain news</li>
    <li><strong>Economy</strong> - Central banks, policy decisions, economic indicators</li>
  </ul>

